           if        f-sts                not  = e-not-err
                     go to crz-arc-orf-600.
       crz-arc-orf-230.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Test sul massimo                                *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        rf-ofr-num-prt       not  = rf-oft-num-prt
                     go to crz-arc-orf-600.
       crz-arc-orf-240.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
