      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           move      spaces               to   w-det-pth-fso-nam      .
           string    "ORDERS_"  delimited by   size
                     w-gen-ann-doc
                                delimited by   spaces 
                     "_"        delimited by   size
                     w-gen-num-doc
                                delimited by   spaces 
                                          into w-det-pth-fso-nam      .
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Determinazione                      *
