      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      "OO"                 to   g-ope                  .
           move      "seq "               to   g-nam                  .
           move      w-det-pth-fso-pt1    to   g-pat                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mcvout"
                                         using g                      .
       crz-arc-orf-350.
