                                         using g                      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Test se invio previsto                          *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        rr-tip-exe           =    03
                     go to crz-arc-orf-900.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Composizione del comando di invio               *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      spaces               to   o-shs                  .
           string    "t_retarus_out "
                                delimited by   size
                     "94.199.91.48 "
                                delimited by   size
                     "siri_vishay "
                                delimited by   size
                     "q7nw3hefzuwfzhwx "
                                delimited by   size
                     w-det-pth-fso-pt1
                                delimited by   spaces
                     " "
                                delimited by   size
                     rr-tip-exe-flg
                                delimited by   size
                                          into o-shs                  .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Chiamata al sistema effettiva                   *
