           move      "CU"                 to   o-ope                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mopsys"
                                         using o                      .
       crz-arc-orf-900.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Chiusura files                                  *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   crz-arc-orf-cls-000  thru crz-arc-orf-cls-999    .
       crz-arc-orf-920.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Test se almeno un ordine da inviare             *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
